description: Redevelopment of site involving the demolition of the buildings and erection of 4no. buildings ranging from one to three storeys in height plus a basement to provide flexible commercial floorspace (Use Class E(g)(iii)) and 27 residential units (Use Class C3), together with the provision of car and cycle parking, refuse storage, hard and soft landscaping and other associated works.
